$Id: BUILDING 23 2005-03-20 19:46:03Z bwolf $

When building a new version, perform the following steps:

1) Read top of scripts/bootstrap.py
2) Download dependencies
3) Edit top of scripts/bootstrap.py
4) Execute scripts/bootstrap.py
5) Update versioncheck.xml to reflect the new version!
6) Update info.plist to reflect the new version!
7) Update InfoPlist.strings to reflect the new version!
8) Start Xcode
9) In the build window choose Deployment
10) Build + test
11) Execute scripts/makedmg.sh and rename the dmg to reflect the new version!
12) Copy the icon from MoinX.app to MoinX.X.Y.Z.dmg!
13) Upload release.
14) Checkout new website.
15) Delete psd's from website.
